This is the give camp project

Pages
  - Login
    - Validation Credentials against CouchDB
  - Registration
    - Create user with e-mail address & Password
  - Ask a question
    - Title, Description, Select a tag

    - UI on top of all of this. 

    - Service endpoint - get
      - createquestion : authenticated
        - List of possible tags along with description
            - TagName
            - TagDescription

    - Service endpoint - post
      - createquestion  : authenticated
        - Title
        - Content
        - Selected tag : TagName
    
  - List of questions by time
      - List of tags to filter with
  - View a question page
    - Add an answer
    - Mark an answer as the accepted answer
    - Vote up/vote down
    - Delete/modify an answer
    - Show ALL the answers on the page
        - Ordered by vote count
        - Show top answer at the top
  - Managing tags page
    - Manage lists
  - Manage users
    - Promotion/moderation

